videos.description: Christian McCaffrey swings out on the wheel route and USC completely losses track of him, allowing Ryan Burns to hit a wide-open McCaffrey and he does the rest going 56 yards to put Stanford up 7-0.
videos.headline: USC forgets to cover McCaffrey as he goes 56 yards for a TD
USC gets on the board with a 47-yard field goal

videos.description: Christian McCaffrey run for 33 yds to the USC 5 for a 1ST down
videos.headline: C. McCaffrey run for 33 yds for a 1ST down

videos.description: Christian McCaffrey run for 1 yd for a TD
videos.headline: McCaffrey dives into endzone for second touchdown on the day

videos.description: Ronald Jones II run for 1 yd for a TD
videos.headline: USC cuts into Stanford lead with 1-yard touchdown run

videos.description: Stanford explodes for another big play when Michael Rector takes the end-around hand off and goes 56 yards to paydirt, putting Stanford up 27-10 on USC.
videos.headline: Stanford goes big-play again, this time Rector for 56-yard TD

videos.description: Ryan Burns pass intercepted Adoree' Jackson return for no gain to the USC 32 STANFORD Penalty, Face Mask (15 yards) (Francis Owusu) to the USC 41
videos.headline: R. Burns pass intercepted,A. Jackson return  for 0 yds,STANFORD penalty, Face Mask (15 yards) (F. Owusu)

videos.description: Stanford's Noor Davis makes the late interception on a ball that goes off USC's Tyler Petite's arm.
videos.headline: Stanford gets the bounce on late interception

videos.description: Christian McCaffrey records 165 rushing yards and two touchdowns in Stanford's 27-10 win over USC.
videos.headline: McCaffrey carries Stanford over USC
